### GET ALL POKEMON
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pokemon

###

### GET ONE POKEMON BY ID
# Replace the ID below with one from the 'Get All' request
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pokemon/65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1

###

### CREATE: BULBASAUR
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pokemon
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bulbasaur",
    "types": ["Grass", "Poison"],
    "level": 5,
    "sprite": "https://img.pokemondb.net/sprites/home/normal/bulbasaur.png"
}

