### UPDATE (PATCH) A POKEMON'S LEVEL
# Change the ID in the URL to a real ID from your DB
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pokemon/65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "level": 50
}

###

### DELETE A POKEMON
# Change the ID in the URL to a real ID from your DB
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pokemon/65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1